overview.longName: Corporacin Inmobiliaria Vesta, S.A.B. de C.V.
overview.longBusinessSummary: Corporacin Inmobiliaria Vesta, S.A.B. de C.V., together with its subsidiaries, acquires, develops, manages, operates, and leases industrial buildings and distribution facilities in Mexico. Corporacin Inmobiliaria Vesta, S.A.B. de C.V. was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Mexico City, Mexico.
